1S pass 3S pass 4S pass pass pass
[Result ""]
{SOUTH has 17 points and might open 1NT. But with the 5-card Major suit she prefers

to open 1♠.

NORTH has excellent ♠ support but with 11 points is not quite strong enough to insist

on reaching game. Instead he makes an invitational jump to 3♠, which SOUTH is strong

enough to raise to game.}
[BCFlags "1f"]
